		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />You should ask Nintendo of America that question (assuming you plan on releasing the title in the US).  I would be interested to see what their response is, given that the console hasn't been on-market since the early-to-mid 90s, and that the case with Tengen never resulted in any kind of &quot;official&quot; statement (and the main focus there had to do with the CIC bypass).<br /><br />Ask 'em.  Seriously.  See what they have to say.

		

		</td>
