	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I think they're more concerned about trademarking than someone selling software/hardware that works on their outdated equipment.  The patents have expired on the NES hardware, it's the trademarks/copywrights on the titles/characters that they hold on to for a long time, or potentially forever in the case of Disney and Mickey Mouse.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


